title: Etran de L'Aïr performs "Agrim Agadez" and more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Etran de L'Aïr performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 7, 2025.

Songs:
Ighre Massina 00:33 
Imouwizla 06:59 
Amidinine 15:27 
Agrim Agadez 23:09 
 
Moussa “Abindi” Ibra - Guitar, Vocals
Abdourahamane “Allamine” Ibrahim - Rhythm Guitar, Vocals, Bass
Abdoulaye “Illa” Ibrahim - Bass, Vocals, Guitar
Alghabid Ghabdouan - Drums

Host: Jyoti Patel
Audio Engineer: Julian Martlew
Guest Audio Engineer: Christopher Kirkley
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz
 
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
